title: Devil Sold His Soul - Discography - Apple Lossless
description:
Devil Sold His Soul are a post-hardcore influenced progressive metal/ambient band from the South of England. Three of the band joined from Mahumodo, thought to be a pioneer of the British hardcore scene. They released their debut full-length album A Fragile Hope on 18 June 2007, having previously toured the UK for several years, along with the release of their debut mini-album Darkness Prevails, produced by Mark Williams.

Both the EP and the Album, in Apple lossless format.
